      h1 Congratulations! Your NodeBB has been set-up.
      | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
      | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
      button#launch.btn.btn-lg.btn-success
        | Launch NodeBB 
        i.fa.fa-spinner.fa-spin.hide
      | &#x9;&#x9;
      p
